YES! we do provide makeup trials. ❤️ You can reach out via DM or Call us on 9664841824.

Reasons you need a makeup trial! 

- To decide on that one makeup artist for your big day can be really exhausting. If you a get trial, your work is done and you are one step closer to find the look. ✨

- Satisfaction, the biggest complaint we get that many makeup artist change the whole complexion while doing makeup. This way you can compare both the sides with and without makeup. ✨

- Trsut, being a bride is stressful enough in all the ways. Through a trial you already know what makeup is look like so there is no anxiety or any surprise element. ✨

- Vibe, an important factor. It’s not always just makeup. Trial gets you to meet them in person before hand. ✨

I believe this is the best way to understand clients. ❤️
